*lilo-22.1-r3 (5 Apr 2002)

  24 Feb 2003; Nicholas Wourms <dragon@gentoo.org> lilo-22.1-r3.ebuild :
  This is definitely not for mips.

  14 Jul 2002; phoen][x <phoenix@gentoo.org> lilo-22.1-r3.ebuild :
